🔐 1. What exactly this role does (Day-to-day)
Create & manage users, roles, authorizations (via PFCG)
Monitor suspicious activity (login failures, privilege misuse)
Work on SoD (Segregation of Duties) violations
Apply SAP security patches (SAP Notes)
Support audits (internal + external)
👉 Think of it as: “protecting SAP systems from misuse + ensuring right access to right people”
